{"tid":2302210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"男人下半身思考佔8成！巨乳妹公開酒店實況：遇過一位腳膠客人","createTime":"2020-11-27T02:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T14:16:45.000Z","uid":38539,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8a5195ea572ac94ce86343161575a3aa84d4d0","tid":2302210,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2oI4DckEJjY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2oI4DckEJjY&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=4b095977\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2oI4DckEJjY</a><br />\n<br />\n常有人說「男人都是下半身思考的動物」，YouTuber「小哥哥艾理」日前就訪問了5位酒店小姐，雖然大部分人認同男人容易「精蟲衝腦」，但也提出不少特例，有的客人時間到就真的回家，或有些客人即使消費了也只要喝茶、聊天，還遇過有人只要「聞腳」。<br />\n<br />\n小哥哥艾理的頻道常拍攝成人話題，他19日上傳的影片向5位酒店小姐詢問「覺得男生都是下半身思考的嗎」，大部分小姐都認為有「百分之80」，也有人說「6成以上，剩下的是沒表現出來」。<br />\n<br />\n有小姐指出，曾經有一位客人玩嗨了，在桌上丟了20萬現金要帶她走，她只能耐心安撫客人並無提供這種服務，再看他「尷尬地把20萬收起來」。不過也有酒店妹坦承，女生如果真的夠喜歡對方，「我會跟他說帶你回家」。<br />\n<br />\n也有人透露，曾遇過客人點了10多位小姐，卻只坐在包廂裡喝茶，要小姐在旁邊做自己的事，或是客人只想「灌小姐酒」，沒有想做其他的事。<br />\n<br />\n有小姐指出，曾遇過有特殊癖好的客人，點檯時就要求她先脫鞋子，看腳漂不漂亮，結果看到喜歡就直接舉起來要舔，「後來每次框我都是為了聞腳」，跟朋友來還要趁別人不注意的時候偷聞，讓艾理聽了也大開眼界。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201127/1863736.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201127%2F1863736.htm&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=87e13da1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201127/1863736.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9e88eb5fa5c2ca1842aa8d1947c321b86fc82aa5","tid":2302210,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"ff88349baf92230335aad4d52f0d40c250cd8d64","tid":2302210,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"宇清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b44251c05662a1020d0c5df9e066ded6e348b6","tid":2302210,"uid":78434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"高汁"},{"pid":"a1e99dfc22306ffab10a824886a91697256ee84b","tid":2302210,"uid":198900,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"樓主 幾時爆肛生單野呀？"},{"pid":"9522857f3b8ef66600b826f897f59c55fb2c56d5","tid":2302210,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:19:58.000Z","msg":"You only listen to your dick instead of your god-damn brain!"},{"pid":"9b734424aade3e12617fba6abc92a195b961068b","tid":2302210,"uid":61653,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:24:45.000Z","msg":"叫雞唔咸濕叫黎托柒咩戇鳩<br />\n利伸：從來唔叫雞"},{"pid":"c582685c49dde666ef00d7028cad5af14332b272","tid":2302210,"uid":366652,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:27:14.000Z","msg":"叫雞唔做愛<br />\n好似去餐廳只係飲水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4f2513d1d0aa5558efd2d7a48d1c121acb6f9d","tid":2302210,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:30:32.000Z","msg":"我叫雞淨係奶閪"},{"pid":"47446dc503ec499f3a00398cbad07b39d4abcec8","tid":2302210,"uid":208823,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a1e99dfc22306ffab10a824886a91697256ee84b","tid":2302210,"uid":198900,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"樓主 幾時爆肛生單野呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"攞完正皮咪走數lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c77d238ed5f01bc23e306a96653f03b05518983","tid":2302210,"uid":179967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"有小姐指出，曾遇過有特殊癖好的客人，點檯時就要求她先脫鞋子，看腳漂不漂亮，結果看到喜歡就直接舉起來要舔，「後來每次框我都是為了聞腳」，跟朋友來還要趁別人不注意的時候偷聞，讓艾理聽了也大開眼界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db